docs.snippet: RIO DE JANEIRO, Aug. 12 (AP). -- President Getulio Vargas began preparations today for the coming visit of President Gabriel Terra of Uruguay, a visit interpreted in some quarters as a step toward exclusive commercial relations among Brazil,...
docs.lead_paragraph: RIO DE JANEIRO, Aug. 12 (AP). -- President Getulio Vargas began preparations today for the coming visit of President Gabriel Terra of Uruguay, a visit interpreted in some quarters as a step toward exclusive commercial relations among Brazil, Argentina and Uruguay.
docs.abstract: To visit Brazil; trade significance seen
